rows.label: qst002901_msg0002
rows.name:
DB Sisters from Larus Trade Guild
follow you here on commission
from Superbian Army.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0003
rows.name:
But thinking about it, it obvious
that only potential customers
crazy enough to come here is you.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0005
rows.name:
Shibushibu can tell that friends
 burdened with something important.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0006
rows.name:
So Shibushibu will graciously let you off
if you help Shibushibu with request.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0007
rows.name:
Shibushibu would like friends
to collect sellable items
from Cliffs of Mors.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0008
rows.name:
Stuff from here very rare in
other countries so DB Sisters
will rake in monies!

rows.label: qst002901_msg0011
rows.name:
This Shibushibu's first time here so not
know exactly what to look for. Just
pick up anything that look valuable.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0101
rows.name:
Anything from Cliffs of Mors make
surefire profit in other countries, so
Shibushibu accept anything you find!

rows.label: qst002901_msg0103
rows.name:
Is not enough yet...
Keep going!

rows.label: qst002901_msg0104
rows.name:
Meh meh!
Friends gathered much stuff!
